[SHORT DESC]
Power doubles with each hit.

[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Deals damage. For every consecutive hit on the opponent, its power doubles, to a maximum Base Power of 160 (reached after four turns). If the user fails to use the move successfully or another move is used, the Base Power resets to 20.</p>

<h2>Competitive Use</h2>
<p>Fury Cutter should not be used competitively. Its Base Power is far too low on the first few turns, and consecutive uses are too difficult to maintain consistently.</p>

<h2>Related Moves</h2>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/megahorn">Megahorn</a> is a more powerful alternative with 120 Base Power and 85% accuracy.</p>
<p><a href="/bw/moves/x-scissor">X-Scissor</a> is a more powerful alternative with 80 Base Power, with no other side effect.</p>